{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came from Algiers or Morocco, I don't know, from North Africa anyhow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they stepped-- stepped forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- I think two or three days after arriving in France, we had visitors, a group, a Parliamentarian groups from Paris came with some I do not know who they were from the government, came down the steps, looked around on that sight.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't a very pleasant sight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were all half-- half-clad, because the heat was enormous and we didn't have much breathing space.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody took off whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- the men were just in underwear, because they just couldn't bear it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They looked at the sight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they read to us in French and then somebody translated in English that they offered us French citizenship as a-- as a sign of their goodwill or so on, because they know that we are refugees and so on.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We should disembark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then one of us, that one particular young Frenchman, stepped forward and explained to them that we are refugees, we are Jewish, and we thank them for their hospitality that they want to offer us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But our way really is to go to our homeland and not in another land again, and nor do we want to be visitors again somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They said that they [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] report that to their government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was-- and that was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was a colossal pressure to disembark, a moral pressure.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Really, we had one Hungarian family that disembarked, much to the phooey and to the-- the whistles of everybody inside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they decided that they can't bear it anymore and they left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, there was a committee.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
